name: Instagram clone for android.
tagline: Make your own Instagram. Fork this repository for basic image sharing android application.
body: ### Welcome to Instagram Clone Android application. This project is basic Instagram application for android devices. Application includes login/logout, share, and delete methods for images. Application supports cloud storage using Parse. ### Authors and Contributors This was my personal project(@karmagamer). ### Support or Contact Visit my website here. for questions or any other feedback.
